{"tid":1630663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足同手足之間 應該要禮貌對話","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:12:54.000Z","uid":183752,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"22d03efe37bd18a2ef0e2fd06594316814e598ab","tid":1630663,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:55.000Z","msg":"而唔係，屌你老母落黎啦 示威呀依加<br />\n更加唔係，吓 和理非仲有咩用<br />\n<br />\n而應該係，手足 不如一齊行落黎，我地依加係示威。<br />\n而應該係，okok 無問題 兄弟爬山。<br />\n<br />\n我唔想分化，我想大家唔好再分化。<br />\nbe humble<br />\n <br />\n前線同和理我都有做，都明果種心情<br />\n所以大家克制下自己 對內 請禮貌<br />\n對外 請屌佢老母 同殺撚佢"},{"pid":"8bd34e43b4a3daa3347f9a3699082f605af88609","tid":1630663,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8bcb1bdb4e328b22ea430690d47b2ac7d38088b1","tid":1630663,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"［最新消息］全民起動 三罷民意調查<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們暫時收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6vUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=39b9ebbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a> 或掃QR code填寫問卷。<br />\n<br />\n民調將於10月11日中午12時結束。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMnfEza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMnfEza.jpg&h=ec657c98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dad38ca2f1df963d208e5a59636a3475217c167","tid":1630663,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"170c587a6854320d47f223689ae041f0ec2fd227","tid":1630663,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b52c87b0855719621e1e86f486f99664478c4ed","tid":1630663,"uid":264915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:15: